    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">策略与动作的终极融合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Tempest Tower》颠覆传统塔防玩法，将经典的基地建设与自由动作战斗完美结合。在建造阶段，探索地图新区域，构筑防御工事；在战斗阶段，迎战成群的爬行怪物，在激战中抢夺资源。你无法始终总览全局，因此务必谨慎布局，智取强敌！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/3619316a376c4cf2be0c8ca8862bdcc6.poster.avif?t=1768408722\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/3619316a376c4cf2be0c8ca8862bdcc6.webm?t=1768408722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/3619316a376c4cf2be0c8ca8862bdcc6.mp4?t=1768408722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">奇械狂想 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Tempest Tower》有着各种疯狂的机械装置，从可以远程歼敌的除虫射击塔，到可以让你在关卡间飞跃的弹跳蹦床，应有尽有，层出不穷！你可以手动触发陷阱对爬行怪物造成范围伤害，也可以部署护盾泡泡将攻击反弹给敌人，各种创意十足的武器数不胜数，个个都能助你力挽狂澜。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/39679b754cca07f0b6451838ccb1c3fd.poster.avif?t=1768408722\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/39679b754cca07f0b6451838ccb1c3fd.webm?t=1768408722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/39679b754cca07f0b6451838ccb1c3fd.mp4?t=1768408722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">逆转战局的道具 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >远行宇宙中的独特植物是你最强的秘密武器！易爆的炸弹浆果可以对一大群敌人造成高额伤害，诱饵灯泡可以引诱爬行怪物进入致命的陷阱，你还可以借助滑翔叶片在巨大的峡谷中翱翔。随机应变，运筹帷幄，利用手头的各种道具克敌制胜。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/c61f1086183aad579ad694cb1c3aef64.poster.avif?t=1768408722\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/c61f1086183aad579ad694cb1c3aef64.webm?t=1768408722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/c61f1086183aad579ad694cb1c3aef64.mp4?t=1768408722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">无尽的尝试 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过无数次的尝试铺就属于你的胜利之路。在开始每个关卡之前都可以自定义装备，抽选机械装置并升级、强化建筑，运用强力的道具组合出疯狂的连击。将危险的关卡元素化为毁灭利器，不断完善你的战术——这里充满了无限可能！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/0f2179732b5d67067effa6440eb25895.poster.avif?t=1768408722\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/0f2179732b5d67067effa6440eb25895.webm?t=1768408722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/0f2179732b5d67067effa6440eb25895.mp4?t=1768408722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">征服每一个关卡  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以敏锐的直觉与反复的试错洞悉每个关卡的精妙之处。在高效防御与经济发展之间找到完美平衡，方能抢占先机。通过难度调节和关卡挑战突破自我极限，冲击终极最高分记录！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123800/extras/524faa663f3fb853ab8ed5f1a3159ae4.avif?t=1768408722\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p>",
